  "title": "Insight HUD",
  "description": "Insight HUD provides two essential HUD overlays that enhance your Minecraft experience with detailed information about entities and your equipment, all while maintaining the vanilla aesthetic.",
  "body": "<h2 data-start=\"44\" data-end=\"61\">Insight HUD</h2>\n<p data-start=\"63\" data-end=\"207\"><strong data-start=\"63\" data-end=\"78\">Insight HUD</strong> is a lightweight mod that enhances your Minecraft experience by displaying essential data in a clean, minimalist overlay.</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"229\" data-end=\"306\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"23\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Gear &amp; Item Insight</strong>: Shows durability and key details of worn or held items in real-time.&zwnj;</span>&nbsp;</li>\n<li data-start=\"229\" data-end=\"306\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"14\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Combat HUD</strong>: While engaged in battle, it tracks your target&rsquo;s health and even displays its loot table</span><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_bc81e9be-2cce-4b55-b2dc-1f28539a1e40.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"381\" height=\"136\"></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_cfb166fb-9300-4bcf-896e-d107ac40e4c1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"336\" height=\"283\"> &nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_64b640e2-c5ee-4401-a8f4-92031b3a01ea.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"411\" height=\"279\"></span></p>\n<h3 data-start=\"621\" data-end=\"642\"><strong>Configuration</strong></h3>\n<ol data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"857\">\n<li data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"715\">\n<p data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"715\">Press <strong>H</strong> (default keybind) to open the <strong data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"714\">Insight HUD Settings</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"716\" data-end=\"793\">\n<p data-start=\"719\" data-end=\"743\">Toggle HUD modules like: GEAR OR ENTITY INFO<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_14db95f4-bdea-4944-b7dc-5e597eee1f9f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"279\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Licenced under MIT</p>",
